com.variant.client

Class VariantError

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.variant.share.error.UserError
      • com.variant.client.VariantError

  • public class VariantError
extends com.variant.share.error.UserError

    User errors, emitted by Variant client. Adapters, wrapping variant client, should extend this class with their own errors in the reserved range 301-400, inclusive.
